<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

  <section class="hero" style="padding-bottom: 60px;">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">About Medprime</span>
      <h1 style="max-width:640px;">Built around one idea: testing shouldn't add stress to an already worrying day.</h1>
      <p class="hero__lead">Medprime Diagnostic Centre opened in 2010 with a single lab and one consulting room. Today we run six specialist departments and a full diagnostic lab, but the goal hasn't changed: fast, accurate answers, explained in plain language.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container grid grid--3">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Accredited lab</h3>
        <p>Every sample is processed in-house by certified technicians using calibrated equipment, with results cross-checked before release.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Specialist doctors</h3>
        <p>Each department is led by a specialist, so your appointment goes to someone trained specifically in that area of care.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Digital-first records</h3>
        <p>Your appointments and reports live in your own patient portal — no more digging through paper folders to find an old result.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%- include('partials/pulse-divider') %>

  <section class="section section--tint">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section__head">
        <span class="section__kicker">Our promise</span>
        <h2>Privacy and accuracy come first</h2>
        <p>Patient data is encrypted at rest in transit-safe form, access-controlled per account, and never shared with a third party without your consent.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
